When using the thread stop function in the detailed view of active service pop-up, if the transaction socket is in Read state it will not be possible to terminate the thread.

This option terminate the thrad after closing the socket Read.

The default value is flase.

When the socket is closed the following information is displayed in Agent log

     2016-02-03 / 18: 12: 49 [INFO] try close active socket of transaction: txid

---

* Default: false
* Type: Boolean
* Restart: required
* Supported Version: 5.0.13